data.description: Are you looking for a home with charm? Add this home to your list!  This home has a side entry into a large mudroom and laundry room, off to the right of this room is an ADDITIONAL MASTER SUITE!! That's right, there is 2 master bedrooms in this home! The living room has nice large windows and hardwood floors! Two of the bathrooms still have unique charm with the original tile! Detached 2 car garage and a large driveway to accommodate parking! This home sits just outside of Richlands City Limits, you get to enjoy are the things close by with no city taxes! No HOA, and so much potential! Book your showing today, this home is a steal!
